aft ausrichten.\r\n(7) Eine Staatsverschuldung muss grundsätzlich vermieden werden.\r\n(8) Die notwendige Daseinsvorsorge für die Bürger muss zu angemessenen Kosten gestaltet sein.\r\n","activityOperationType":"SELF_OPERATED","clientOrganizations":[],"clientPersons":[],"codexViolation":false,"disclosureRequirementsExist":false,"donationInformationRequired":true,"donators":[{"categoryType":"DONATIONS","description":"es handelte sich um eine Spende ","donationEuro":{"from":90001,"to":100000},"fiscalYearEnd":"12/21","fiscalYearStart":"01/21","name":"natürliche Person"}],"employeeCount":{"from":11,"to":20},"fieldsOfInterest":[{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG","de":"Bundestag","en":"Bundestag"},{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG|FOI_BUNDESTAG_LEGAL","de":"Rechtsstellung der Abgeordneten","en":"Legal status of member of parliament"},{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG|FOI_BUNDESTAG_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Bundestag“","en":"Other in the field of “Bundestag”"},{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG|FOI_BUNDESTAG_PARLIAMENTARY","de":"Parlamentarisches Verfahren","en":"Parliamentary procedure"},{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG|FOI_BUNDESTAG_VOTE","de":"Wahlrecht","en":"Suffrage"},{"code":"FOI_ECONOMY","de":"Wirtschaft","en":"Economy"},{"code":"FOI_ECONOMY|FOI_ECONOMY_CONSUMER_PROTECTION","de":"Verbraucherschutz","en":"Consumer protection"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_LAWS","de":"EU-Gesetzgebung","en":"EU legislation"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Europapolitik und Europäische Union“","en":"Other in the field of “European politics and the EU”"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_POLITICS","de":"Institutionelle Fragen der EU","en":"Institutional questions of European politics"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION","de":"Europapolitik und Europäische Union","en":"European politics and the EU"},{"code":"FOI_LAW","de":"Recht","en":"Law"},{"code":"FOI_LAW|FOI_LAW_LEGAL","de":"Rechtspolitik","en":"Legal policy"},{"code":"FOI_LAW|FOI_LAW_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Recht“","en":"Other i